{"tid":2514103,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完不忘單野，其實係唔係成條金巴利街都唔食得？","createTime":"2021-05-03T04:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T13:12:28.000Z","uid":393710,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b436b14ea044fd31814d866ece1b0d81fbb8517c","tid":2514103,"uid":393710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"有時係果度食Lunch，好好彩無食過不忘<br />\n<br />\n有Ching話果度鼠患好嚴重，其實情況係點<br />\n一間鋪頭有鼠患，可能成條街都有<br />\n而家都唔敢去果度食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留番比老鼠食埋我個份，我叫第二度外賣算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8437ae157c0028db2b188879a5520e6b7e16428","tid":2514103,"uid":278184,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n全港都係咁<br />\n鼠患呢d好難解決<br />\n鼠王芬都搞唔撚掂啦<br />\n但一定冇佢果間咁誇張"},{"pid":"e7797f37c0270870ac0ea2afe3fa867c414a21b7","tid":2514103,"uid":22500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"果頭食環做左滅鼠已經好左好多。<br />\n要睇本身間餐廳街生做成點！"},{"pid":"01ef0896d5046245e7ae2a5eec3f67eb737281d3","tid":2514103,"uid":277659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"金巴利街街市垃圾站餐廳齊晒<br />\n你話冇老鼠就假啦"},{"pid":"276da8d7cdbab20f552f9b568d05b3de4848dcc0","tid":2514103,"uid":393710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"01ef0896d5046245e7ae2a5eec3f67eb737281d3","tid":2514103,"uid":277659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"金巴利街街市垃圾站餐廳齊晒<br />\n你話冇老鼠就假啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"姐係老鼠踩完附近垃圾房，過黎餐廳踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n永久Blacklist<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a94ef9a46db226441b6dc31d0947458df71dfb4","tid":2514103,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"嗰條街好似大部份泡菜嘢<br />\n唔係鍾意韓